Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.40,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:05.44,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:08.67,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.57,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case takes place in\Na department store at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The empty floors after closing time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:15.66,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even under the cover of night,\Nthere is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have you now, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Send him to hell, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:09.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Yaiba, shall defend world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:22.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm in high school. So what\Nam I doing watching this drivel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like Yaiba, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:31.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it! Go, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Talk about fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:49.48,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thank you for shopping with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:54.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We look forward to seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:03.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba! Yaiba! He fights for justice! Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba's autograph is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:14.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to treasure it for my entire life, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:21.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we took the picture with Yaiba,\NI seem to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:23.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the picture, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:27.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:33.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to recall Genta saying that he was hungry when we took this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:40.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I bought a hot dog and then—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:44.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's at that shop! I'm going to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:48.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the place is closed by now.\NI say leave it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:52.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want! I'm going to go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:55.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. My deductive skills are to blame for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:14.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry! The security system\Nis going to activate in 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:21.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. That door's going to lock\Nwhen the security system activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:24.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get it in less than 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:25.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! My treasure's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s great detective skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this was nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We better hurry before the\Nsecurity system activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the security guards'\Noffice inside the building
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and explain the situation,\NI'm sure they'll let us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security Office! Floor B2!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamen Yaib—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The jewelry store's on the 6th floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And there are antiques in the\Nconvention hall on the 7th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the elevator lady—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. We have until morning\Nto take whatever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gang of thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble if they find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:50.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill us! Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the elevator lady\Nand those other people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:57.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's stay hidden\Nand contact the police! OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! There's no dial tone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cord's been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:16.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use this phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. It doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:23.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The phones must be down\Nbecause of the security system!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So nobody's going to come to rescue us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat a ton of eel\Nlunches before I get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to give up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Please notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:59.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The robbers will hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:03.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, it won't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:08.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up! The windows here\Nare made of especially thick glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security office! There's a weird sound\Ncoming from the 7th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:41.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:45.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Use the security cameras\Nto check out the 7th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan! What about the window?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:57.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! You won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing strange that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing strange?! Those were\Nsome pretty loud sounds we heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's take the loot and split!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Let's check it out just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:19.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, aren't there any exits around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, you little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:44.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:47.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko and I got caught up in a discussion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make dinner right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've seen our faces! Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security office! Do you read me?!\NTurn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? I didn't copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.16,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's a bunch of little brats in the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd those lousy kids go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.46,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey! What's going on?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:50.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The other guys in the security\Noffice know we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They turned on the lights to catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} still hasn't come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know where that lousy kid is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:15.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta! Get out! Everyone out! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:34.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They almost had us trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Save that for after we get out of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Conan was at the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he go with his friends\Nto see some kids' show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitch dark outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try calling the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my food, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to starve me to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.66,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is Marutan Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.39,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We are currently closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:27.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We need to get as far away\Nfrom them as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:35.29,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We will be open during our regular\Nhours tomorrow, from 10 AM—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:42.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? So what do you say you\Nmake me some dinner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Kojima household? This is Ran Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:47.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:11:59.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there! This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have this department store surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your weapons down and release the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:27.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no police here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:33.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:38.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They used a bunch\Nof stupid mannequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let 'em get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:48.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Yoshida residence?\NI'm Conan Edogawa's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} hasn't come home yet either?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:58.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a call from Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s family too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:02.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:13.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, Genta! Do you want them to catch you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:29.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I just realized something strange,\Nbut I don't know what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan and his friends were kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's the only explanation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:15.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Did any of their families\Nreceive ransom demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is that they're taking\Ntheir sweet time coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be back soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's about some dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:38.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Cook me some food already—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the investigation department?\NInspector Megure, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:49.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Works better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real liability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:15:00.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:08.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you at such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any incidents at the moment\Nthat might involve the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:19.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is strange that none of\Nthem have returned home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could something have happened to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put out a bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they'll turn up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:33.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now if you'll excuse me,\NI'm in the middle of an important case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've done all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All there is to do now is wait\Nfor any reports about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to do this at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:16:00.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us. We'll pay for this\Nif we make it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:05.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we even will make it out alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so down, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had plenty to eat now, so cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:15.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take care of them\Nand get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Detective Boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:30.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it must be a pretty important case\Nif they're still at it this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:33.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nand the others aren't important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn that Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:46.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm missing my dinner thanks to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A gang of department store thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:55.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sneak in after the stores close\Nand steal jewelry and electronics...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:59.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the important\Ncase he was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Department store?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Commence counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now where are they hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:47.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't handle alcohol well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay! We can't let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:25.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:52.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:57.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Aha! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:04.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, elevator lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:11.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, we're in danger—\Nthere are some bad people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's going on, elevator lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:27.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, the 5th member of the thief gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:30.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:34.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a 5th person who\Nactivated the escalator earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This person had been waiting\Nto catch all four of us at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:40.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the remaining people\Nin the security office,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:44.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you were the only one who knew\Nhow many of us there were.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:49.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned in advance to get inside\Nby getting a job as an elevator girl
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you could scout out the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:58.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent deductive work, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:02.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems you didn't know that\NI was actually the gang's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A pistol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair that you have a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:09.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}OK! I'll lure her onto the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:34.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The game's over, little boy! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Basketballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your pointless resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:15.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:46.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the thieves! Take them into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:50.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:53.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of silly kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:55.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:39.13,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The following day, we were\Ngiven an award ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:41.03,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}for capturing the thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:43.03,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We didn't have to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:47.17,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}for any of the things we ate\Nor broke inside the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:52.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chalk another one up—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:24.00,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:24.00,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode's hint right after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:04.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:07.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It came from her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:09.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.13,0:24:14.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we were taping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:15.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:20.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder might be recorded on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:23.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So that was the one who\Nsmeared her dress with blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:30.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:35.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Medicine capsule
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.02,0:24:38.23,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time is quite difficult too!
